\u201cMaster and disciple(s)\u201d <\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5e\u0f72\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f56\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5e\u0f72\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f60\u0f56\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f54\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cFarmers and nomads\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The same principle applies in the spoken language for abridging personal names of four syllables:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5a\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f62\u0fa1\u0f7c\u0f62\u0f0b<\/span> Tsedor = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5a\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f72\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f62\u0fa1\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f97\u0f7a\u0f0b<\/span> Tsering Dorj\u00e9<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f40\u0fb2\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f54\u0f63\u0f0b<\/span> Trapel = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f40\u0fb2\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f54\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f63\u0fa1\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span> Trashi Penden<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f7c\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f58\u0f0b<\/span> Ch\u00f6gyam = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f7c\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> Ch\u00f6kyi Gyatso (or Gyamtso)<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f92\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f53\u0f0b<\/span> S\u00f6dr\u00f6n = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f53\u0f58\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f92\u0fb2\u0f7c\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b<\/span> S\u00f6nam Dr\u00f6lma<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">Note that in some cases, a resyllabification occurs whereby the prefixed or the superscribed letter of the following syllable is interpreted as the final of the preceding syllable. The written orthography records this phenomenon. For example, the last letter in Ch\u00f6gyam or Tsedor belongs in fact to the fourth syllable (that has been omitted), respectively <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f97\u0f7a\u0f0b<\/span>.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">Graphic abbreviations consist of using special signs to replace a group of letters. The following are the most common:<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">The circle<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> \u0f1a<\/span>, written above a letter, replaces the suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58<\/span>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f7e\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f58\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">The <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f4a\u0f0b<\/span> (reversed <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f4f\u0f0b<\/span>) substitutes for the suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f4a\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f7a\u0f4a\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f63\u0f7a\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b <\/span><\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">There are also abbreviations in which two syllables are graphically compacted into a single syllable:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f74\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cGirl\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f5a\u0f74\u0f7c\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f5a\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cHour\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f40\u0fb2\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f51\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f7a\u0f4a\u0f0b<\/span> = <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f40\u0fb2\u0f0b\u0f64\u0f72\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f51\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f7a\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span><\/li> <\/ul>","title":""}]}
